  "intent": "Execute a droplet digital PCR preparation protocol involving transfer of 180\u00b5L DPBS to columns 1-8 of prep plate, followed by 20\u00b5L article addition to column 1 with mixing. Perform 1:1 serial dilution across columns 1-7 using 20\u00b5L transfers with thorough mixing at each step. Transfer 40\u00b5L from column 6 to column 8 and mix with 180\u00b5L volume. Dispense 20\u00b5L master mix into columns 1-5 of final plate, then transfer 5\u00b5L samples from prep plate columns 6-8 to final plate columns 1-3. Complete with 5\u00b5L water additions to final plate columns 4-5.",
